n: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuu danh thu Carragher tai xuat sau su co phun mua vao fan MU hinh anh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Carragher t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t sau s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 phun m\u01b0a v\u00e0o fan MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/cc-7692-1522828358.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Carragher xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean k\u00eanh TV3 Sport c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. \u1ea2nh: NS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Carragher b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n sau scandal khi\u1ebfn anh m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0 Juventus g\u1eb7p Real Madrid ng\u00e0y 4/4. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng s\u1edbm kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean - chuy\u00ean gia Carragher sau khi video anh nh\u1ed5 n\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ecdt v\u00e0o xe h\u01a1i \u0111i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh. Chuy\u00ean gia c\u1ee7a ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh Monday Night Football ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i sau khi Liverpool thua MU 1-2 ng\u00e0y 10/3. Carragher bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i xin l\u1ed7i tr\u00ean truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh hai ng\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb Sky Sports c\u1eaft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 40 tu\u1ed5i ph\u00e2n tr\u1ea7n: \"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 g\u00ec, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec c\u00f4 g\u00e1i 14 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb m\u1eafc k\u1eb9t trong cu\u1ed9c c\u00e3i v\u00e3 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u1edbi b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a c\u00f4\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, k\u00eanh TV3 Sport c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn kh\u00e1c. Peter Norrelund, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a MTG Sport - \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a k\u00eanh, cho r\u1eb1ng Carragher b\u1ecb tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ee7 cho sai l\u1ea7m. \"Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Jamie xin l\u1ed7i gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 anh ta c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed1i tho\u1ea1i\", Peter Norrelund n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ngoisao.net<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"827","checkdouble":"183579"},{"date":"15:31 05/04","title":"Gia \u0111\u00ecnh ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u00ec si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Ronaldo","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/gia-dinh-phan-khich-vi-sieu-pham-cua-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"826","checkdouble":"183580"},{"date":"15:44 05/04","title":"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Quang H\u1ea3i \"cho\u00e1ng\" tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1ch trang \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c l\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/5/tien-dao-quang-hai-choang-truoc-cach-trang-diem-khac-la-cua-ban-gai.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer d