   </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadt L\u00ea thay \u0111\u1ed5i phong c\u00e1ch trang \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00ean tr\u00f4ng l\u1ea1 h\u01a1n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nKh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u00e0y, Nh\u1eadt L\u00ea th\u00e1o m\u1eaft k\u00ednh v\u00e0 trang \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm n\u00ean tr\u00f4ng c\u00f4 b\u1ea1n r\u1ea5t cu\u1ed1n h\u00fat v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t Nh\u1eadt L\u00ea s\u1edf h\u1eefu n\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p r\u1ea5t T\u00e2y v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch trang \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh khoe g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t trang \u0111i\u1ec3m xinh \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt L\u00ea nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01a1n 14k like c\u00f9ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn chia s\u1ebb. Trong h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m comment khen ng\u1ee3i b\u1ed7ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t comment c\u00f3 n\u1ed9i dung l\u00e0 l\u1ea1 h\u00fat \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n 1k like. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnh ch\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n \"l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c\" c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau. T\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ebd khen ng\u1ee3i hay n\u00f3i l\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau m\u00e1t l\u00f2ng m\u00e1t d\u1ea1, Quang H\u1ea3i ph\u00e1n: \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ai? Tr\u1ea3 Lu l\u1ea1i cho t\u00f4i? (Lu l\u00e0 t\u00ean th\u00e2n m\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt L\u00ea).<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1eeba h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba t\u1ecf ra kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i khi xem \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau khi\u1ebfn d\u00e2n t\u00ecnh th\u00edch th\u00fa.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang Quang H\u1ea3i m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n trai n\u00e0o khi nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 th\u00f4i!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTheo kenh14.vn<br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"825","checkdouble":"183581"},{"date":"14:40 05/04","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP TPHCM vs SLNA 19h00 ng\u00e0y 5/4 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/truc-tiep-tphcm-vs-slna-19h00-ngay-54-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weig