lor:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00e1c phe v\u00e9 tr\u00e0n ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u1ed1 Tr\u1ecbnh Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, nh\u01b0ng xem ch\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL ch\u01b0a hot nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League</span>, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1edf Th\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u, nh\u1eefng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n Thanh, hay Quang H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Duy M\u1ea1nh s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, BTC k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e9 b\u00e1n ra \u1edf trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, &ldquo;v\u1ee1 s\u00e2n&rdquo; hay ch\u00ed \u00edt l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i tr\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y. Tuy nhi\u00ean 4 ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd b\u00f3ng l\u0103n, s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9 v\u00f2ng 3 V-League v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Mua v\u00e9 h\u1ea3 em \u01a1i&rdquo; &ndash; M\u1ed9t trong r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi phe v\u00e9 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o, ngay khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eeba b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ph\u1ed1 Tr\u1ecbnh Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, con ph\u1ed1 t\u1ecda l\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/bau-hien-chi-khung-quyet-lam-moi-san-hang-day-khong-kem-san-nha-cua-psg-168-183010.html\" target=\"_blank\">SV\u0110 H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby</span> v\u1eabn kh\u00e1 v\u1eafng v\u1ebb, v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ha Noi vs HAGL Ve tran dau chua sot hinh anh\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL V\u00e9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a s\u1ed1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/IMG_7981.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4 ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u: V\u00e9 tr\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL ch\u01b0a hot nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ho\u1eb7c nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn b\u00f3ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby, m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n d\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n c\u00e1ch tr\u00ean con ph\u1ed1 C\u00e1t Linh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ecf \u0111i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0o s\u00e2n h\u01a1n, thay v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i v\u00f2ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua h\u1ed9 v\u00e0i chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i A \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft s\u1ea1ch v\u00e9. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u1eeda d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c C\u0110V trung l\u1eadp, c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean t\u00e1c nghi\u1ec7p. Ph\u00eda b\u00ean kia, kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i B l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u00e0nh cho C\u0110V ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sau m\u1ed9t l\u00fac hoang mang, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea7y b\u00e1n v\u00e9 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi r\u1eb1ng mua v\u00e9 \u1edf kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i B v\u00e0&hellip; ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e2u c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. M\u1ed7i m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 50 ngh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed3ng. C\u1ea7m trong tay nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i y\u00ean t\u00e2m th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o cho b\u1ea1n m\u00ecnh, sau \u0111\u00f3 ra v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n v\u00e9 s\u1ebd &ldquo;\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&rdquo; l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 h\u01a1n, t\u1eeb gi\u1edd cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-ha-noi-vs-hagl-19h00-ngay-54-vleague-2018-372-183576.html\" target=\"_blank\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL</span> b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 (5/4).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ha-noi-vs-hagl-19h00-ngay-54-cho-bua-tiec-bong-da-tai-hang-day-168-183554.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/17/ha-noi-vs-hagl-19h00-ngay-54-cho-bua-tiec-bong-da-tai-hang-day.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ha-noi-vs-hagl-19h00-ngay-54-cho-bua-tiec-bong-da-tai-hang-day-168-183554.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL (19h00 ng\u00e0y 5/4): Ch\u1edd b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby</span><br>\r\nHai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9 v\u00f2ng 3 V-League? \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 NHM \u0111ang...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ecdng Hi\u1ebfu &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"822","checkdouble":"183578"},{"date":"15:50 05/04","title":"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/ha-noi-vs-hagl-co-hoi-cuoi-cho-cong-phuong.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContai