dding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111inh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay.</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9 v\u00f2ng 3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League </span>gi\u1eefa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby t\u1ed1i nay s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3n m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng Park Hang Seo. Vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y Park d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb r\u1ea5t tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo du khan tran cau dinh Ha Noi vs HAGL hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111inh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/hlv-park-hang-seo-xem-quang-hai-duy-manh-thi-dau-o-vong-1-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1edbi H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111inh H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ef1 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Quang H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng,... nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai CLB \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadp danh s\u00e1ch chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ASIAD 2018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Indonesia v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV Park ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u00f4ng s\u1ebd l\u00ean danh s\u00e1ch kho\u1ea3ng g\u1ea7n 60 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd r\u00fat d\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u1eadp danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd\u00a0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n nh\u1eb1m ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c g\u1ea5p b\u1ed9i b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n khi ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o n\u00e0o t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-ha-noi-vs-hagl-19h00-ngay-54-vleague-2018-372-183576.html\" target=\"_blank\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL</span> s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i nay 5/4 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ha-noi-vs-hagl-co-hoi-cuoi-cho-cong-phuong-168-183582.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/2/ha-noi-vs-hagl-co-hoi-cuoi-cho-cong-phuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ha-noi-vs-hagl-co-hoi-cuoi-cho-cong-phuong-168-183582.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng?</span><br>\r\nHAGL b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 3 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 v\u0169 kh\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"820","checkdouble":"183586"},{"date":"15:42 05/04","title":"\"Th\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League, c\u00f2n h\u01a1n thua chung k\u1ebft C1\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/tha-vo-dich-europa-league-con-hon-thua-chung-ket-c1.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px