c\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xa l\u1ea1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, khi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2009/10 v\u00e0 2011/12. HLV Simeone \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111em ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee9 3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang h\u1ecd&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Argentina m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u. &ldquo;H\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1eb7c \u00edt, ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu Atletico g\u1eb7p <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Bayern-Munich-1567.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bayern Munich</span> ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd n\u00f3i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Astana, h\u1ecd n\u00f3i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Simeone \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Atletico v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League\" title=\"Simeone Europa League\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/tha-vo-dich-europa-league-con-hon-thua-chung-ket-c1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Simeone \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Atletico v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, b\u1edfi b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c 100% b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Sporting, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t HLV v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd CLB c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Atletico, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 2 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, b\u1edfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 lu\u00f4n \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, thay v\u00ec l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft C1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua&rdquo; &ndash; Diego Simeone k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Arsenal-4.html\">Arsenal</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ee7 an to\u00e0n, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Atletico v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League s\u1ebd g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/nhan-dinh-atletico-madrid-vs-sporting-lisbon-02h05-ngay-64-europa-league-201718-344-183559.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/nhan-dinh-atletico-madrid-vs-sporting-lisbon-02h05-ngay-64-europa-league-201718.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/nhan-dinh-atletico-madrid-vs-sporting-lisbon-02h05-ngay-64-europa-league-201718-344-183559.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Atletico Madrid vs Sporting Lisbon 02h05 ng\u00e0y 6/4 (Europa League 2017/18)</span><br>\r\nAtletico Madrid vs Sporting Lisbon l\u00fac 02h05 ng\u00e0y 6/4 (L\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i Europa League/c\u00fap C2 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2017/18): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"819","checkdouble":"183577"},{"date":"15:57 05/04","title":"3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm c\u1ee7a Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juve","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/5/3-yeu-to-lam-nen-chien-thang-dam-cua-real-truoc-juve.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-wei