y v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb khi \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho m\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n M.U v\u00e0 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00f3c x\u00f9 c\u0169ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Mourinho d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd quay l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n MU mua Willian thay Mata \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford th\u00f4ng qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Willian thay Mata trong mua he toi hinh anh\" title=\"MU mua Willian thay Mata trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/23/MU-mua-Willian-thay-Mata-trong-mua-he-toi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\">MU mua Willian thay Mata trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y<br>\r\n            </span></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM.U s\u1ebd chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Willian. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00fang nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Chelsea b\u1ecf ra cho Shakhtar Donetsk \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 5 n\u0103m. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Willian v\u1edbi The Blues c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a t\u1edbi, M.U quy\u1ebft x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League c\u00f9ng Man City. C\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn, \u1eaft c\u00f3 k\u1ebb ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, Mourinho g\u1ecdi t\u00ean <span href=\"bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mata-quyet-pha-hong-ke-hoach-cua-man-city-172-183414.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Juan Mata</strong></span>. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 30 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4 t\u1edbi ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t\u201d v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn nay v\u1eabn v\u1eadt l\u1ed9n trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Mata s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng n\u00f3. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1eebng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i CLB m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 h\u01a1n 4 n\u0103m qua. Tuy nhi\u00ean, chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i hay \u1edf kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 do m\u00ecnh anh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. M\u1ed9t khi M.U \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Mata b\u00e1m tr\u1ee5 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/bayern-dem-tin-vui-cho-mu-vu-james-rodriguez-193-183422.html\">Bayern \u0111em tin vui cho M.U v\u1ee5 James Rodriguez</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-va-real-nhan-tin-mung-vu-sao-psg-172-183384.html\">M.U v\u00e0 Real nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng v\u1ee5 sao PSG</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-va-liverpool-mua-domingos-quina-172-183371.html\">M.U v\u00e0 Liverpool tranh gi\u00e0nh sao tr\u1ebb tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/samuel-umtiti-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-180-183369.html\">Sao Barca l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng gi\u1eefa tin \u0111\u1ed3n s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-mua-lucas-hernandez-cua-atletico-madrid-180-183303.html\">Barca nh\u1eafm \u201ch\u00e0ng hot\u201d ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba M.U cu\u1ed7m Umtiti</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"817","checkdouble":"183571"},{"date":"14:59 05/04","title":"Wenger: \"Lacazette kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh sau khi \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/15/wenger-lacazette-khong-con-la-chinh-minh-sau-khi-den-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adC