ity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Leonardo Jardim \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 4 n\u0103m  t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Monaco. V\u00e0 theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 Yahoo Sport  UK \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n Jardim thay Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng sau khi m\u00f9a  gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 n\u00e0y k\u1ebft th\u00fac.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi  th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t c\u1ee7a Chelsea, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Antonio Conte r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o  m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu. Trong danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m  qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u00f3 Leonardo Jardim c\u1ee7a Monaco, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft h\u1ecd  t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ligue 1 v\u00e0 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLeonardo  Jardim tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t thay th\u1ebf Antonio Conte ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng  t\u1ea1i Chelsea. N\u0103m nay 43 tu\u1ed5i, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua  m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 4 t\u1ea1i Monaco v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u00f4ng  c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c PSG \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ligue 1 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn  lu\u00f4n gi\u1ea3i HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea muon Jardim thay Conte mua he toi hinh anh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n Jardim thay Conte m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Chelsea-muon-Jardim-thay-Conte-mua-he-toi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Conte nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p  \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Jardim v\u1edbi Monaco c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2020 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0111i\u1ec1u  kho\u1ea3n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng 7,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c CLB mu\u1ed1n h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c. C\u1ef1u  thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Sporting Lisbon \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i Monaco, h\u00e0i  l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1eed  s\u1ee9c \u1edf m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 danh gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1ec1 nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd  b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh\u201d,  Jardim cho bi\u1ebft h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. \u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c  s\u1ef1 l\u00e2u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y b\u1edfi lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh. \u00dd t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y t\u1edbi  gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c l\u1edbn h\u01a1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea nham Jardim\" title=\"Chelsea nham Jardim\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/chelsea-muon-jardim-thay-conte.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n Jardim thay Conte t\u1eeb m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, nh\u01b0ng \u00edt CLB ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Monaco v\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea  mu\u1ed1n Jardim thay Conte v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do t\u1ef7  ph\u00fa Roman Abramovich l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng b\u1ecb xem l\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu tham v\u1ecdng.  M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, Jardim s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n  c\u1ea3i t\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\