und:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfc xe bus c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a Liverpool t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng chai l\u1ecd v\u00e0 ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Anfield. V\u00e0 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh ph\u00eda The Kop.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xe bus cua Man City bi tan cong boi fan Liverpool hinh anh\" title=\"Xe bus c\u1ee7a Man City b\u1ecb t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1edfi fan Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/fan-liverpool-bi-chi-trich-du-doi-vi-tan-cong-xe-bus-cua-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Xe bus c\u1ee7a Man City b\u1ecb t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1edfi C\u0110V\u00a0Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 vang d\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City t\u1ea1i Anfield. L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra, c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p khi t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng xe bus c\u1ee7a Man City. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u00e1o s\u00e1ng, chai l\u1ecd v\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u1eadt th\u1ec3 l\u1ea1 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e9m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda xe bus c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, 2 c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong khi ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n c\u00e1c C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Man City c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i thu\u00ea m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe bus kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Steven Gerrard \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n hung d\u1eef \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c C\u0110V Liverpool l\u00e0m v\u1eeba qua\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00eda Liverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t Merseyside \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cLiverpool l\u00ean \u00e1n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh vi tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn khi\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc xe bus c\u1ee7a Man City b\u1ecb h\u01b0 h\u1ecfng tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn Anfield. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n xin l\u1ed7i HLV Pep Guardiola, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City, c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 quan ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u00e0nh vi qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m. \u01afu ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p cho Man City m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft\u201d.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/guardiola-thua-liverpool-03-nao-phai-tham-hoa-184-183549.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/guardiola-thua-liverpool-03-nao-phai-tham-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/guardiola-thua-liverpool-03-nao-phai-tham-hoa-184-183549.html\">Guardiola: \u201cThua Liverpool 0-3 n\u00e0o ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda\u201d</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh b\u1edfi c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Klopp c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i The Citizens sau \u0111\u00f3: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p nh\u01b0 v\u1eady x\u1ea3y ra. Khi xe bus c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111i qua, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh nh\u1ea5t t\u1edbi Man City v\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u1eeba qua\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng xe bus Man City c\u1ee7a C\u0110V\u00a0Liverpool:\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xe bus cua Man City bi tan cong boi fan Liverpool hinh anh\" title=\"Xe bus c\u1ee7a Man City b\u1ecb t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1edfi fan Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/111350-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xe bus cua Man City bi tan cong b