-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c d\u00e0nh cho Pep\u201d \u2013 Roy Keane n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Liverpool 3-0 Man City.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1eabn bi\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a The Kop, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p Man City \u2013 CLB xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 Liverpool 3-0 Man City \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ch\u1ec9 sau 30 ph\u00fat, v\u1edbi c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Chamberlain, Mane v\u00e0 \u201cTh\u00e1nh\u201d Salah. Theo huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, Roy Keane, th\u00ec Man xanh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi th\u1ed5i ph\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng cho Man City, r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc hay g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u00e0i test cho s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, r\u1eb1ng Man xanh c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m\u201d \u2013 Roy Keane cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 Pep Guardiola c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch. H\u1ecd ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool 3-0 Man City huyen thoai MU het loi ca ngoi kinh dich hinh anh\" title=\"Liverpool 3-0 Man City huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/qua-an-tuong-huyen-thoai-mu-het-loi-ca-ngoi-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roy Keane chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Liverpool 3-0 Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y Man City \u0111ang b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o h\u1ecd l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn khi th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn 3 b\u00e0n. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n, t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng Man City ngh\u0129 \u00edt ra h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cV\u1edbi to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, Man City x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Liverpool c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Liverpool. S\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cLiverpool c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng Man City, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Milner, Henderson, Chamberlain \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 s\u1ef1 mong \u0111\u1ee3i khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn 3-0.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Anfield, Roy Keane cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t: \u201c\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ghi 1 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 th\u1ebf l\u00e0 xong.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Liverpool 3-0 Man City<br>\r\n</strong><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/14088663/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Liverpool vs Man City<br>\r\n</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/henderson-bay-to-noi-that-vong-sau-tran-dai-thang-man-city-184-183563.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Man City, sao Liverpool v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng n\u00e3o n\u1ec1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/huyen-thoai-canh-bao-liverpool-sau-man-vui-dap-man-city-184-183562.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Liverpool sau m\u00e0n v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/guardiola-thua-liverpool-03-nao-phai-tham-hoa-184-183549.html\">Guardiola: \u201cThua Liverpool 0-3 n\u00e0o ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-vs-man-city-duoi-got-giay-vua-ai-cap-172-183545.html\">Liverpool \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p Man City: D\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3t gi\u00e0y \u201cVua Ai C\u1eadp\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-30-man-city-con-benh-giao-dieu-cua-pep-guardiola-184-183544.html\">Liverpool 3-0 Man City: C\u01a1n b\u1ec7nh gi\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tung-bung-vui-dap-man-city-klopp-van-tuc-gian-184-183542.html\">T\u01b0ng b\u1eebng v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Man City, Klopp v\u1eabn... t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"810","checkdouble":"183567"},{"date":"12:17 05/04","title":"Liverpool 3-0 Man City: Xin ch\u00e0o, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Anfield!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/5/liverpool-30-man-city-xin-chao-day-la-anfield.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin: