border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea1n ngh\u0129 g\u00ec v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c n\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh? Hai CLB xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9? Ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n sai, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-vs-man-city-duoi-got-giay-vua-ai-cap-172-183545.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool 3-0 Man City</span>.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Man xanh c\u00f2n l\u00e2u m\u1edbi ch\u00edn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u00e0 tr\u00ean to\u00e0n c\u00f5i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. H\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au-c184-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Champions League</span>.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chamberlain ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City\" title=\"Liverpool 3-0 Man City Xin ch\u00e0o, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Anfield! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/120200-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chamberlain ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Man xanh (v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Liverpool) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho 90 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. B\u1edfi \u00edt ra n\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Man United &ndash; th\u00ec 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110em nh\u1eefng tinh t\u00fay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ra tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng&hellip;</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u00e1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Premier League, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111ang \u0111\u1ebfm ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Manchester-United-1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man United</span>. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1eefa, v\u00e0 Pep Guardiola s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean khi ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3, n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eadp cho tan x\u00e1c t\u1ea1i Anfield, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf h\u00f3a th\u00e2n th\u00e0nh Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ho\u00e0ng l\u1eeda \u0111\u1ec3 thi\u00eau r\u1ee5i nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch hung h\u00e3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi th\u1ed5i ph\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng cho Man City, r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc hay g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u00e0i test cho s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, r\u1eb1ng Man xanh c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m&rdquo; &ndash; Roy Keane, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/qua-an-tuong-huyen-thoai-mu-het-loi-ca-ngoi-liverpool-184-183567.html\" target=\"_blank\">huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU cho r\u1eb1ng Man xanh ch\u1ec9 \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 gi\u1ecfi</span>.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool 3-0 Man City\" title=\"Liverpool thang Man City 3-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/qua-an-tuong-huyen-thoai-mu-het-loi-ca-ngoi-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man xanh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u00edn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng ch\u00ednh L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf, d\u00f9 b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, l\u1ea1i \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh CLB ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t Cup C1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i (31 b\u00e0n sau 9 tr\u1eadn). \u0110\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Man City c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/gabriel-jesus-148191.html\" target=\"_blank\">Gabriel Jesus</span> c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 6 pha ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong hi\u1ec7p 1. V\u00e0 3 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Brazil th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u1edf ch\u1ea5m giao b\u00f3ng gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Liverpool 3-0 Man City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-liverpool-30-man-city-184-183541.html\" target=\"_blank\">th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc</span>, ho\u1eb7c th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u1edf Bundesliga tu\u1ea7n v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, khi Bayern Munich v\u00f9i d\u1eady Borussia Dortmund (th\u1eadt tr\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 2 CLB c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp). C\u00f9ng nhau chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, c\u1ea3 2 c\u00f9ng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay, ch\u00ednh t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Pep trong tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City\" title=\"S\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Pep trong tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/pep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>S\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Pep trong tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><strong> Anfield ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t</strong></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng, th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/man-city-1471.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City</span> &quot;\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p&quot; Liverpool t\u1ea1i Champions League. T\u1ea1i sao l\u1ea1i v\u1eady? B\u1edfi v\u00ec Man xanh d\u00f9 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecd nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen th\u1ebf n\u00e0o ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 anh nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0i n\u0103m, l\u00e0 g\u00e3 h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Cup C1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 th\u1ebf, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Liverpool 3-0 Man City l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c th\u1ee9 179, nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean 2 \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf Cup ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. V\u00e0 h\u00e3y xem, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu DNA Champions League? Ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Liverpool, v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 15 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 10/2014 (th\u1eafng 10, h\u00f2a 5).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng, ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Man City b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, b\u1edfi l\u00e0m g\u00ec c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu &ldquo;n\u1eb1m y\u00ean&rdquo; cho h\u1ecd &ldquo;t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng&rdquo; nh\u01b0 \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 khi anh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ebd t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu. Man City v\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen v\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 &ldquo;l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf&rdquo; c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n &ndash; hay d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u, l\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c, l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh ph\u1ea3i trui r\u00e8n qua \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. 30 ph\u00fat, 3 b\u00e0n thua, Man xanh v\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 may m\u1eafn m\u1edbi gi\u00fap h\u1ecd r\u1eddi Anfield v\u1edbi t\u1eebng \u1ea5y b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool 3-0 Man City s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i\" title=\"C\u0110V Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/120443-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u0110V Liverpool lu\u00f4n mang trong m\u00ecnh DNA chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool, m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c lu\u00f4n tr\u1ed3i s\u1ee5t qua t\u1eebng \u1ea5y m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ch\u1eb3ng ai d\u00e1m xem th\u01b0\u1eddng &ldquo;DNA Champions League&rdquo; c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Real Madrid 4-0 c\u0169ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 10 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Anfield c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Real &ndash; PSG \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, khi m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ecb xem th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 h\u00e0o nho\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a g\u00e3 tr\u1ecdc ph\u00fa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Jurgen Klopp c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi n\u1eafm \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2015, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng cho L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf? Ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Anfield.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 bi\u1ebft b\u00e0i h\u00e1t truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Man City l\u00e0 g\u00ec kh\u00f4ng? Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9 g\u00ec, nh\u01b0ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\">&ldquo;You&rsquo;ll Never Walk Alone&rdquo;</span> th\u00ec nghe qua r\u1ed3i ch\u1ee9? C\u00e1c C\u0110V Man xanh lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u l\u00e0 &ldquo;fan phong tr\u00e0o&rdquo;, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf tr\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Etihad \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 &ldquo;Empty-had&rdquo;, v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 City l\u00e0m g\u00ec c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0 fan c\u1ee7a The Kop.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anfield trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Liverpool 3-0 Man City\" title=\"Anfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/120450-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Anfield nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm Man City trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0 khi ai \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Man City th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c, \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng ti\u1ec1n s\u1eb7c m\u00f9i d\u1ea7u m\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n Pep Guardiola, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd &ldquo;ng\u1ed3i m\u00e2m tr\u00ean&rdquo; v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Liverpool hay Man United t\u1ea1i Cup C1. C\u00f2n \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Man xanh qu\u00e1 l\u1eafm c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n PSG m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t, v\u00e0 ngang nhau v\u1ec1 c\u00e1i g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, Jurgen Klopp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p, sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Liverpool 3-0 Man City:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&ldquo;Xin ch\u00e0o, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Anfield!&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Liverpool 3-0 Man City</div>\r\n<div><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/14088663/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Liverpool vs Man City</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/qua-an-tuong-huyen-thoai-mu-het-loi-ca-ngoi-liverpool-184-183567.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU: Man City ch\u1ec9 gi\u1ecfi \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"art